ent-Z14STWeaponRifleA545 = A-545 "Balalaika"
    .desc = Assault rifle with balanced recoil system. Rare in the Zone, usually comes with military expeditions. Nicknamed 'Balalaika' for distinctive sound. It uses 5.45x39mm ammo.
    .suffix = Z14, Custom

ent-Z14STWeaponRifleAK74M = AK-74M "Modern"
    .desc = Modern modification with polymer furniture and optics rail. Valued in the Zone for versatility and improved ergonomics. It uses 5.45x39mm ammo.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14STWeaponRifleAKS74 = AKS-74
    .desc = Classical folding assault rifle chambered in 5.45x39mm. Main weapon of military and stalkers in the Zone. Reliable as hammer but requires skill for accurate fire.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14STWeaponRifleAKS74Green = AKS-74 (Forest)
    .desc = Variant with green polymer furniture. Ideal for operations in northern forest areas of the Zone. It uses 5.45x39mm ammo.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14STWeaponRifleAKS74U = AKS-74U
    .desc = An AKS-74 with cosmetic changes. It uses 5.45x39mm ammo.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14STWeaponRifleAKS74UBlack = AKS-74U (Night)
    .desc = An AKS-74 with a shiny black finish. It uses 5.45x39mm ammo.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14STWeaponRifleAKS74USERAPH = AKS-74U "Emerald"
    .desc = A worn-out AKS-74U pulled from the scrap heap and given new life by Zone gunsmiths, then finished in green. Unreliable and inaccurate, but better than going unarmed. It uses 5.45x39mm ammo.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14STWeaponRifleAKS74UWhite = AKS-74U (Winter)
    .desc = An AKS-74 with a matte white finish like fresh snow. It uses 5.45x39mm ammo.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14STWeaponRifleSaiga545 = saiga 5.45 "Hunter"
    .desc = Civilian version of AK-74M with fixed stock. Popular among stalkers for reliability and ammo availability. It uses 5.45x39mm ammo.
    .suffix = Z14
